Package: geospatialsuite
Title: Comprehensive Geospatial Analysis and Advanced Visualization Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Olatunde D.", "Akanbi", email = "olatunde.akanbi@case.edu", role = c("aut", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7719-2619")), person("Vibha", "Mandayam", role = "aut"), person("Yinghui", "Wu", role = "aut", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3991-5155")), person("Jeffrey", "Yarus", role = "aut", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9331-9568")), person("Erika I.", "Barcelos", email = "erika.barcelos@case.edu", role = c("aut", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9273-8488")), person("Roger H.", "French", email = "roger.french@case.edu", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6162-0532")))
Maintainer: Roger H French <roger.french@case.edu>
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for geospatial analysis featuring 40+ vegetation 
    indices, advanced raster visualization, universal spatial mapping, water quality
    analysis, CDL crop analysis, spatial interpolation, temporal analysis, and 
    terrain analysis. Includes efficient visualization using tidyterra, RStoolbox,
    and native terra plotting. Designed for agricultural research, environmental
    monitoring, remote sensing applications, and publication-quality mapping with
    support for any geographic region and robust error handling.
